#PressPlay: Get y’all popcorn ready, Chance the Rapper’s new movie drops today in theaters across the country! “Chance the Rapper’s Magnificent Coloring World” marks the first time an artist has independently distributed a film to theatres.
________
“Magnificent Coloring World” is a concert film self-distributed through Chance the Rapper’s House of Kicks production company and film house.
________
Chance wrote, produced, edited and starred in the film, working hard this past year to bring never-before-seen footage to his fans. The footage was filmed in 2017 right before Chance took home 3 Grammys for his critically acclaimed mixtape “Coloring Book.”
________
Fans will be able to see the film in person for a limited time in several cities including Los Angeles, New York, Chicago, Detori, Las Vegas and Philly.

node.title: Chance The Rapper’s Film Released Today

TSR Staff: China! @china_lovelace
__________________________
#TSRExclusiveDetails: #Roommates, earlier tonight, the tea was flowing as #FalynnPina got some things off her chest about her ex-husband #SimonGuobadia. As we reported, in a series of posts, she claimed that Simon stalks her, posts subliminal captions about her & her man #JaylanBanks & sends packages to her home. 
__________________________
Well, we reached out directly to Jaylan, and he brought the receipts! He alleges that the drama has been going on for months and that he & Falynn changed their numbers and moved from her previous Sandy Springs, GA townhome. The couple now lives in Duluth. However, the move didn't stop the alleged harassment from Simon. Jaylan claims that Simon sent packages to him & the expectant mother of his child’s home on August 24th while they were out of town. 
__________________________
“God knows how this dude got the address to our new house,” he explained. Jaylan agreed that Simon’s behavior is odd. He said, “You know how us men like to act in the beginning like we not hurt but deep down we are.” In addition to the packages being sent to the couple’s home, Jaylan claims whenever he & Simon happen to be at the same club, there is drama there too. He claims when he walks into a venue, Simon leaves within 5-10 mins. He also alleges that Simon alerts the owners to try and prevent Jaylan from entering. Thoughts #Roomies 👀 (SWIPE)
